---
title: Easy Chicken, Leek & Silverbeet Risotto with Grated Parmesan
description: Pop on your uggies, pull out your favourite blanket and get super cosy with the ultimate comfort dish. With tender chicken,
punchy garlic paste and Parmesan, we're betting you'll be in love with this risotto way before the last bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-chicken-leek-silverbeet-risotto-54a71bb2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/easy-chicken-leek-silverbeet-risotto-60c071121ee7c7015301a433-7d02e046.pdf
